<h1>Configuration files of NuTyX</h1>
 
 <h2>The keyboard</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/vconsole
   <li>
    /etc/X11/xorg.xonf.d/20-keyboard.conf
  </ul>
 <h2>The network and machine name</h2>
<ul>
 <li>
  /sys/class/net/
 <li>
  /etc/systemd/network
 <li>
  /etc/systemd/network/10-default.network
 <li>
  /etc/wpa_supplicant.&lt;name_of_the_wifi&gt;
 <li>
  /etc/resolv.conf
 <li>
  /etc/hostname
</ul>
 <h2>The language</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/profile.d/i18n.sh
  </ul>
 <h2>Geographical position or region</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/localtime
  </ul>
 <h2>Partition mounting locations, USB keys, NFS, exchanges partitions, etc</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/fstab
  </ul>
 <h2>The clock</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/adjtime
  </ul>
 <h2>Boot of the machine</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /boot/grub/grub.cfg
  </ul>
 <h2>Manual kernel modules loading and loading parameters</h2>
 <ul>
  <li>
   /etc/modules-load.d/
  <li>
   /etc/modprobe.d/
 </ul>
 <h2>Files and folders creation (normaly temporair) at boot time</h2>
 <ul>
  <li>
   /etc/tmpfiles.d
 </ul>
 <h2>Services launch scripts locations</h2>
 <ul>
  <li>
   /etc/systemd/
 </ul>

<h2>User's scripts location</h2>
 <ul>
  <li>
   /home/&lt;username&gt;/.bashrc
  <li>
   /home/&lt;username&gt;/.bash_profile
 </ul>
 <h2>SDDM graphical Login</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/sddm.config
  </ul>
 <h2>GDM graphical Login</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/gdm/custom.conf
  </ul>
 <h2>lightdm graphical Login</h2>
  <ul>
   <li>
    /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf
  </ul>
